00:09:41,647 --> 00:09:44,750
"with all thy heart, with all thy soul

63
00:09:44,750 --> 00:09:46,652
"and with all thy mind.

64
00:09:46,652 --> 00:09:50,756
"This is the first and great commandment", right?

