I'm not supposed to tell you, but I will.

83
00:10:54,053 --> 00:10:55,354
I didn't ask for anything.

84
00:10:55,354 --> 00:10:57,823
I just told God how much I loved my grandparents

85
00:10:57,823 --> 00:10:59,458
and my father.

86
00:10:59,458 --> 00:11:02,228
- Now isn't that nice?

87
00:11:02,228 --> 00:11:05,931
- Lord, thank you for our family and for this special day.

88
00:11:05,931 --> 00:11:07,600
Continue to guide us and teach us

89
00:11:07,600 --> 00:11:10,036
through your word and your Spirit.

90
00:11:10,036 --> 00:11:13,139
In your Son's precious name, amen.

91
00:11:13,139 --> 00:11:15,341
- Amen, thanks, dad.

92
00:11:15,341 --> 00:11:17,243
- You're welcome good night.

93
